{"blogid": "123954054", "writerAge": "码龄3年", "writerBlogNum": "7", "writerCollect": "9", "writerComment": "0", "writerFan": "0", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "81", "writerName": "君临天下101", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_123954054.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "121178", "writerRankWeekly": "350248", "writerThumb": "1", "writerVisitNum": "4543", "blog_read_count": "2948", "blog_time": "于 2022-06-01 20:29:38 发布", "blog_title": "Linux中mysql密码修改方法（亲测可用）", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h2><a id=\"mysql_0\"></a>前提：安装mysql</h2>\n<ul><li>解压mysql.tar.gz到指定目录</li><li>进入mysql-5.7.18目录</li><li>创建文件夹mkdir data</li><li>创建用户来执行mysqld命令</li></ul>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">groupadd</span> mysql   <span class=\"token comment\"># 创建组mysql</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">useradd</span> -g mysql mysql\t<span class=\"token comment\"># 创建用户，并指定组</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul><li>初始化数据库，在bin目录下<br/> ./mysqld --initialize --user=mysql --datadir=/opt/mysql-5.7.18/data --basedir=/opt/mysql-5.7.18</li></ul>\n<h2><a id=\"mysql_14\"></a>修改mysql密码</h2>\n<p>1.首先启动mysql<br/> 启动MySQL服务，mysql-5.7.18/bin目录下执行命令：./mysqld_safe &amp;<br/> （其中&amp;符号表示后台启动）</p>\n<p>2.登录mysql<br/> 登录进入mysql，mysql-5.7.18/bin目录下执行命令：./mysql -u root -p<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\195849ca5d144c49a6a6b00e5ebb4ff6.png\"/><br/> 输入原密码进入即可</p>\n<p>3.设置密码</p>\n<ul><li>set password=password(‘123456’);</li><li>此处’123456’即为所设置新密码</li><li>在mysql中输入命令必须带有；结尾<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\889e47502ac04280929be1325284af87.png\"/></li></ul>\n<h3><a id=\"_30\"></a>授权远程访问</h3>\n<p>执行授权命令：grant all privileges on <em>.</em> to root@‘%’ identified by ‘123456’;<br/> 更新权限信息，执行flush刷新权限: flush privileges;<br/> 关闭防火墙：systemctl stop firewalld<br/> 查看防火墙状态：systemctl status firewalld</p>\n<h3><a id=\"_36\"></a>远程连接数据库访问</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ced41aa824f64e98bfea9d560fd52b34.png\"/></p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "SQL", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 0, "time": "2022-06-01 20:29:38", "summary": "前提：安装解压到指定目录进入目录创建文件夹创建用户来执行命令创建组创建用户，并指定组初始化数据库，在目录下修改密码首先启动启动服务，目录下执行命令：其中符号表示后台启动登录登录进入，目录下执行命令：在"}